answers.answer: I'm having my third and I'm surprised I'm already showing!
Sorry posted early - my uterus is pretty high up as well.
Just wondering how you know your uterus is up high?
Pressed down until I find it... In retrospect I think I was also bloated as things have settled now and it's more normal level:)

Mine is up to belly button now, but had scan today and no twins and blood test shows normal sugars for now. Feel from your pubic bone, it will be hard and keep following it up till it ends. When you orgasm or have braxton hicks your uterus becomes solid which can also help identify it!

question: This is my third pregnancy and I'm 8w5d. I've discovered my uterus is about just over halfway between pubic bone and belly button. I don't remember it being this high up with my 2nd.I've googled and there appear to be 2 viable reasons. 1 diabetes or 2 twins. I had gestational diabetes with my 2nd so thinking this may be the reason...
title: uterus position 2nd+ time mummies
